# node toolchain
node_modules/

# local env overrides
*.local

# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored — the built SPA is vendored into
# the repo so the single `evva` binary embeds a working UI without a node
# build step at install/release time (go install + release.yml run `go build`
# only). Rebuild with `npm run build` and commit dist/ after frontend changes.
